title: Early NFL Win Totals, Browns chatter with John Breech (Football 4/2)
description:
Will Brinson and John Breech discuss the latest news and notes around the NFL, including Tom Brady's April Fool's Day joke, the Browns trading Emmanuel Ogbah to the Chiefs and then they look at some early NFL win totals released by Las Vegas.
